      \uC54A\uC74C"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 790123393310822
    m_Localized: "\uBAAC\uC2A4\uD130 \uC2A4\uD0AC\uB85C \uC678\uBD80\uC5D0 \uB4DC\uB7EC\uB098\uC9C0
      \uC54A\uC74C"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 790123393310823
    m_Localized: 'Damage: Launches a sword energy wave and deals damage equal to
      <b><color=#F75D32>500%</color></b> of ATK to the enemy.

      Special Effect
      : The sword energy travels to the end of the map.

      AoE: 3 tiles forward
      on the X-axis.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 790123393310824
    m_Localized: "Damage : Swings a scythe widely, dealing damage equal to <b><color=#F75D32>500%</color></b>
      of ATK to the enemy. \nSpecial Effect : Enemies hit will have their ATK SPD
      <b><color=#F75D32>reduced by 50%</color></b>\nfor <b><color=#F75D32>3 seconds.</color></b>\nAoE
      : 3 tiles forward on the X-axis."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 790123393310825
    m_Localized: "Effect : Grants allies a shield equal to <b><color=#F75D32>1000%</color></b>
      of Mensha\u2019s ATK for <b><color=#F75D32>4 seconds</color></b> \nAoE : Same
      row as Mensha."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 790123393310826
    m_Localized: "Damage : Deals magic damage equal to <b><color=#F75D32>300%</color></b>
      of ATK. \nSpecial Effect : The Skill ATK <b><color=#F75D32>increases by 150%</color></b>against
      the enemies with fire synergy.\nTarget : Nearest enemy."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 790123393310827
    m_Localized: 'Damage : Summons a flame bean and deals damage equal to <b><color=#F75D32>350%</color></b>
      of ATK.

      Special Effect : Leaves residual heat in AoE, dealing <b><color=#F75D32>75%</color></b>
      damage per second for<b><color=#F75D32>2 seconds.</color></b>

      AoE: 3x3
      area centered on the nearest enemy.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 790123393310828
    m_Localized: "Damage : Fires a shotgun and deals damage equal to <b><color=#F75D32>400%</color></b>
      of Philia\u2019s ATK.\nSpecial Effect : If an enemy is killed by the skill,\nSkill
      Cooldown is reset immediately. \nTarget : Nearest enemy."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 790123393310829
    m_Localized: "Damage : Deals damage equal to <b><color=#F75D32>850%</color></b>
      of ATK. \nSpecial Effect : Enemy hit is \n <b><color=#F75D32>knocked back</color></b>
      by two tiles. \nTarget : 1 enemy with the highest ATK."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 790123393310830
    m_Localized: "Damage : Strikes forcefully and deals damage equal to <b><color=#F75D32>250%</color></b>
      of ATK. \nSpecial Effect : Enemies hit are afflicted with <b><color=#F75D32>Silence
      Debuff for 3 seconds.</color></b>\n<color=#77889A><b><color=#F75D32>*</color></b>Silence
      : Skill Usage Disabled, Skill Cooldown Reduction Halted</color>\nTarget : Nearest
      enemy."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 790123393310831
    m_Localized: "Damage : Summons flames and deals damage equal to <b><color=#F75D32>450%</color></b>
      of ATK.\nSpecial Effect : If the enemy hit has a shield,\ndestroys the enemy\u2019s
      shield immediately. \nAoE : 3x3 area centered on Rukida."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 790123393310832
    m_Localized: 'Effect : Increases the ATK by <b><color=#F75D32>30%</color></b>
      for<b><color=#F75D32>3 seconds.</color></b>

      Target : 2 allies with the
      highest ATK.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 790123393310833
    m_Localized: "Effect : Recovers all allies\u2019 HP by <b><color=#F75D32>500%</color></b>
      of Enki\u2019s ATK, and increases the ATK SPD by <b><color=#F75D32>40%</color></b>
      for \n<b><color=#F75D32>2 seconds.</color></b>\nTarget : All allies."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 790123393310834
    m_Localized: "Damage : Equal to <color=#F75D32>500%</color> of Tetora\u2019s
      ATK + increased damage proportional to Magic DEF.\nEffect : Swings the greatsword
      and deals damage to 1 enemy, knocking the enemy back by <color=#F75D32>4 tiles.</color>\n
      \nSpecial Effect : If the knocked-back enemy collides with a structure or character,
      the enemy is stunned for <color=#F75D32>1.5 seconds</color> in a 3*3 area\nand
      take additional damage equal to <color=#F75D32>200%</color> of ATK+damage proportional
      to Magic DEF. \n \nAoE : Nearest enemy."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 790123393310835
    m_Localized: "Damage : Launches a grenade at the enemy and deals damage equal
      to <color=#F75D32>250%</color> of ATK. The grenade detonates after targeting
      the enemy, dealing additional <color=#F75D32>150%</color> damage to the area.
      \nTarget : 3 enemies with the lowest current HP."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 790123393310836
    m_Localized: "Damage: Deals damage equal to <color=#F75D32>250%</color> of ATK
      to nearby enemies and knocks them back in a cross-shaped area outward. \nEffect
      : Grants a <color=#F75D32>50%</color> DEF Up Buff to self for <color=#F75D32>4
      seconds.</color> \nBonus Effect : Increases Phys DEF by additional <color=#F75D32>25%</color>
      for each Wind Synergy unit deployed.\n(Max: 3 units) \n \nAoE : Cross-shaped
      area centered on self."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 790123393310837
    m_Localized: "Effect : Seals the enemy in a coffin for <color=#F75D32>3 seconds.</color>
      Sealed enemy can still be targeted, but their Skill Cooldown will not progress.
      \nTarget : Enemy with the highest ATK."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 790123393310838
    m_Localized: "Damage : Deals damage equal to <color=#F75D32>500%</color> of Adria\u2019s
      ATK, and the damage increases proportional to<color=#F75D32>Phys DEF</color>.\nBonus
      Effect : Enemies within the AoE are stunned for <color=#F75D32>1 second.</color>\nAoE
      : Self-Centered."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 790123393310839
    m_Localized: "Effect : Summons a bear for {0} seconds. Upon summoning, deals
      damage equal to {1}% of Pippin\u2019s ATK in a 3*3 area centered on the bear.
      The summoned bear casts a taunt that lasts for {0} seconds in 3*3 area. \nBear
      Stats : 200% of Pippin\u2019s HP, 70% of Pippin\u2019s ATK, all other stats
      are identical to Pippin. \nTarget : Enemies around the target Pippin is currently
      attacking."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 790123393310840
    m_Localized: "AoE : 1 tile, 3 tiles, 5 tiles, 7 tiles forward. \nEffect : Unleashes
      multiple firearms over a wide area, striking <color=#F75D32>10 times</color>
      over <color=#F75D32>3 seconds</color>, with different damage based on the AoE
      range.\nDamage : \n-1 and 3 tiles forward: damage equal to <color=#F75D32>900%</color>
      of ATK per strike\n-5 tiles forward: damage equal to <color=#F75D32>700%</color>
      of ATK per strike\n-7 tiles forward: damage equal to<color=#F75D32>500%</color>
      of ATK per strike."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 790123393310841
    m_Localized: "Damage : Throws a boomerang at the enemy and deals damage equal
      to <color=#F75D32>300%</color> of ATK. \nIf there is another enemy near the
      target hit, the boomerang bounces to that enemy.\nEach time boomerang bounces,
      its damage reduces by <color=#F75D32>50%.</color>\nThe boomerang can hit up
      to <color=#F75D32>5 enemies.</color>\nBonus Effect : ATK SPD increases by <color=#F75D32>10%</color>
      for 2 seconds per enemy hit. \nTarget: Nearest enemy."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 790123393310842
    m_Localized: 'Effect : Drops a vial, reducing healing effects of enemies within
      range by <color=#F75D32>60%</color>

      and Phys DEF by <color=#F75D32>80%</color>
      for <color=#F75D32>3 seconds.</color>

      Target : 3*3 area around the enemy
      with the highest Phys DEF and Magic DEF.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 790123393310843
    m_Localized: Explosion
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 790123393310844
